onospace; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(87, 166, 74); font-style: italic; line-height: 26px;\">#Left,&nbsp;&nbsp;将一个或多个值插入到列表头部(左部)，</span><br/>lpush&nbsp;key&nbsp;value1&nbsp;[value2]&nbsp;……<br/><span style=\"color: rgb(87, 166, 74); font-style: italic; line-height: 26px;\">#&nbsp;rpush是从尾部插入</span><br/>rpush&nbsp;key&nbsp;value1&nbsp;[value2]&nbsp;……<br/></code></pre><ul class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; width: 1088.31px; padding-left: 25px;\"><li><section>获取数据</section></li></ul><pre style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"><code style=\"overflow-x: auto; padding: 16px; background: rgb(30, 30, 30); color: rgb(220, 220, 220); display: -webkit-box; font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(87, 166, 74); font-style: italic; line-height: 26px;\">#获取列表指定范围内的元素</span><br/>lrange&nbsp;key&nbsp;start&nbsp;stop&nbsp;<br/><br/>lindex&nbsp;key&nbsp;index<br/><span style=\"color: rgb(87, 166, 74); font-style: italic; line-height: 26px;\">#&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;获取列表长度</span><br/>llen&nbsp;key&nbsp;<br/></code></pre><ul class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; width: 1088.31px; padding-left: 25px;\"><li><section>获取并移除数据</section></li></ul><pre style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"><code style=\"overflow-x: auto; padding: 16px; background: rgb(30, 30, 30); color: rgb(220, 220, 220); display: -webkit-box; font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(87, 166, 74); font-style: italic; line-height: 26px;\">#&nbsp;lpop从左侧头部删除一个元素</span><br/>lpop&nbsp;key&nbsp;<br/><span style=\"color: rgb(87, 166, 74); font-style: italic; line-height: 26px;\">#&nbsp;rpop从右侧头部删除一个元素</span><br/>rpop&nbsp;key<br/></code></pre><p style=\"padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; line-heig