 8px; line-height: 26px; color: black;\">获取集合数据总量</p></section></li></ul><pre style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"><code style=\"overflow-x: auto; padding: 16px; background: rgb(30, 30, 30); color: rgb(220, 220, 220); display: -webkit-box; font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 12px;\">zcard&nbsp;key<br/>zcount&nbsp;key&nbsp;min&nbsp;max<br/></code></pre><ul class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; width: 1088.31px; padding-left: 25px;\"><li><section>集合交、并操作</section></li></ul><pre style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"><code style=\"overflow-x: auto; padding: 16px; background: rgb(30, 30, 30); color: rgb(220, 220, 220); display: -webkit-box; font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 12px;\">zinterstore&nbsp;destination&nbsp;numkey skey&nbsp;[key&nbsp;...]<br/>zunionstore&nbsp;destination&nbsp;numkeys key&nbsp;[key&nbsp;...]<br/></code></pre><p style=\"padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; line-height: 26px;\"><strong>效果</strong></p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" src=\"http://www.tp6.com/download_img/20231028/WeChat_1698473285.png\" style=\"display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"/><h3 style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 20px;\">sorted set类型数据的扩展操作</h3><ul class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; width: 1088.31px; padding-left: 25px;\"><li><section>获取数据对应的索引（排名）</section></li></ul><pre style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"><code style=\"overflow-x: auto; padding: 16px; background: rgb(30, 30, 30); color: rgb(220, 220, 220); display: -webkit-box; font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 12px;\">zrank&nbsp;key&nbsp;member<br/>zrevrank&nbsp;key&nbsp;member<br/></code></pre><ul class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; width: 1088.31px; padding-left: 25px;\"><li><section>score值获取与修改</section></li></ul><pre style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"><code style=\"overflow-x: auto; padding: 16px; background: rgb(30, 30, 30); color: rgb(220, 220, 220); display: -webkit-box; font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 12px;\">zscore&nbsp;key&nbsp;member<br/>zincrby&nbsp;key&nbsp;increment&nbsp;member<br/></code></pre><p style=\"padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; line-height: 26px;\"><strong>使用场景:</strong></p><ul class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; width: 1088.31px; padding-left: 25px;\"><li><section>各类资源网站TOP10（电影，歌曲，文档，电商，游戏等）</section></li><li><section>聊天室活跃度统计</section></li><li><section>游戏好友亲密度<strong style=\"color: black;\">分析</strong></section></li></ul><blockquote style=\"border-top: none; border-right: none; border-bottom: none; font-size: 0.9em; overflow: auto; color: rgb(106, 115, 125); padding: 10px 10px 10px 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px; border-left-color: rgb(239, 112, 96); background: rgb(255, 249, 249);\"><p style=\"font-size: 16px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; color: black; line-height: 26px;\">为所有参与排名的资源建立排序依据</p></blockquote><p style=\"padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; line-height: 26px;\"><strong>示例:</strong></p><pre style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"><code style=\"overflow-x: auto; padding: 16px; background: rgb(30, 30, 30); color: rgb(220, 220, 220); display: -webkit-box; font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(87, 166, 74); font-style: italic; line-height: 26px;\">##&nbsp;文档热度排序&nbsp;</span><br/>zadd&nbsp;wordset&nbsp;10&nbsp;word001&nbsp;30&nbsp;word002&nbsp;40&nbsp;word003&nbsp;90&nbsp;word005&nbsp;80&nbsp;word006&nbsp;70&nbsp;word007<br/><span style=\"color: rgb(87, 166, 74); font-style: italic; line-height: 26px;\">##&nbsp;获取正序排序</span><br/>zrank&nbsp;wordset&nbsp;word005<br/><span style=\"color: rgb(87, 166, 74); font-style: italic; line-height: 26px;\">#&nbsp;获取倒叙排序</span><br/>zrevrank&nbsp;wordset&nbsp;word005<br/><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(87, 166, 74); font-style: italic; line-height: 26px;\">#&nbsp;分数加</span><br/>zincrby&nbsp;wordset&nbsp;2&nbsp;word005<br/></code></pre><p style=\"padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; line-height: 26px;\"><strong>效果:</strong><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" src=\"http://www.tp6.com/download_img/20231028/WeChat_1698473308.png\" style=\"display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\"/></p><h4 style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 18px;\">sorted set类型数据操作的注意事项</h4><ul class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; width: 1088.31px; padding-left: 25px;\"><li><section>score保存的数据也可以是一个双精度的double值，基于双精度浮点数的特征，可能会丢失精度，使用时候要慎重</section></li><li><section>sorted_set底层存储还是基于set结构的，因此数据不能重复，如果重复添加相同的数据，score值将被反复覆盖，保留最后一次修改的结果</section></li></ul></section>', 'uploads/img/2023-10/b305c1d057a8d00b8781456c4c081256.jpg', 'uploads/thumb/2023-10/b075299d82e48c7423b576a8a8269d7d.jpg', '', '1', '0', '0', '1', '1', '0', '100', '', '1697471344', '1698473834');
INSERT INTO `cy_article` VALUES ('39', '3', '1', '0', 'admin', 'fasdfasdfasdfasf', 'mysql', 'fasdfasdfasdf', 'fasdfasdfasdfsadfsdfsdf', '<p style=\"text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;\"><span class=\"js_jump_icon h5_image_link\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" src=\"http://www.tp6.com/download_img/20231028/WeChat_1698471442.jpeg\" width=\"678\" height=\"577\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 678px; height: auto !important;\"/></span></p><blockquote style=\"text-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 10px 10px 10px 20px; outline: 0px; border-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-right-style: solid; border-bottom-style: solid; border-color: rgba(64, 184, 250, 0.4); color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: inherit; overflow: auto; text-size-adjust: inherit; line-height: 1.55em; border-radius: 6px; background: rgba(64, 184, 250, 0.1);\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 0.9em; outline: 0px; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 84, 84); outline: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">Redis分布式存储的常见方案有：<br/></span></p><section><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 84, 84); outline: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">1.「主从 (Master-Slave) 模式</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 84, 84); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">」</span>主从复制，读写分离，数据备份。</span></section><section><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 84, 84); outline: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">2.「哨兵 (Sentinel) 模式</span><span style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 84, 84); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">」</span>一主多从，哨兵监控，自动处理故障，容错和恢复。</span></section><section><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 84, 84); outline: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">3.「&nbsp;集群 (Cluster) 模式</span><span style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 84, 84); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">」</span>多主多从，数据分片，在线扩容。</span></section><section><span style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><br/></span></section><section><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 84, 84); outline: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">Redis集群切片的方式有：</span></section><section><span style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(85, 84, 84); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">1.「客户端分片」</span><span style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">分片逻辑在Redis客户端实现，采用一致性哈希来决定Redis节点。</span></section><section><span style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(85, 84, 84); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">2.「中间件分片」</span><span style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">借助中间件实现Redis节点的路由分派，根据路由规则将请求发送到正确的Redis节点上。</span></section><p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 84, 84); outline: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">3.&nbsp;「客户端服务端分片」</span><span style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Redis Cluster模式，客户端采用一致性哈希，服务端提供错误节点的重定向服务。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><br/></span></p><section><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 84, 84);\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">本文将详细介绍「Redis分布式存储</span><span style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">」<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">的3种方案</span></span>和「Redis集群切片<span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">」</span>的3种常见方式。</span></span></section></blockquote><h2 style=\"text-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; outline: 0px; font-size: 22px; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-bottom: 4px solid rgb(64, 184, 250);\"><span style=\"margin-bottom: -22px; outline: 0px; display: flex; width: 20px; height: 20px; background-size: 20px 20px; background-image: url(&quot;https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ZfyQPSha5X8EXvgrCpDyhrAoOko6Mwicgpp3TuwW3YoPJpJqfEqryDG3IIdcbdx9LJhCOqDXCq9u1J1uSSVgVHQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;);\"><br/></span><span style=\"margin-left: 25px; outline: 0px; display: flex; color: rgb(64, 184, 250); font-size: 20px;\">什<span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">么是Redis集群</span></span></h2><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">Redis集群是由多个redis实例组成的集合，将缓存的数据分散到多个redis节点上存储，减轻单个缓存节点的访问压力，达到分流效果，提高了存储容量和吞吐量，提供高可用性和容错恢复能力，实现了水平扩容。</span></p><h2 style=\"text-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; outline: 0px; font-size: 22px; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-bottom: 4px solid rgb(64, 184, 250);\"><span style=\"margin-bottom: -22px; outline: 0px; display: flex; width: 20px; height: 20px; background-size: 20px 20px; background-image: url(&quot;https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ZfyQPSha5X8EXvgrCpDyhrAoOko6Mwicgpp3TuwW3YoPJpJqfEqryDG3IIdcbdx9LJhCOqDXCq9u1J1uSSVgVHQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;);\"></span><span style=\"margin-left: 25px; outline: 0px; display: flex; color: rgb(64, 184, 250); font-size: 20px;\">R<span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">edis<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">集群的作用和优势</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"></span></span></span><span style=\"margin-left: 25px; outline: 0px; display: flex; color: rgb(64, 184, 250); font-size: 20px;\"></span><span style=\"margin-top: -10px; outline: 0px; display: flex; width: 200px; height: 10px; border-top-left-radius: 20px; background: rgba(64, 184, 250, 0.5); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; justify-content: flex-end; float: right;\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 164, 231);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">处理大规模数据</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">：<span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">将数据分散在多个节点上，从而突破单节点内存限制，有效应对数据量的增长和高并发的访问请求。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 