ot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;\">Master节点负责数据的写操作，Slave节点负责数据的读操作。<br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;\">通过主从复制，将Master节点的数据变更同步到Slave节点。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(1, 171, 255);\">「主从模式的优点」</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color